Specifying the Length of a List
-------------------------------

<br>

\begin{code}
{-@ measure length @-}
length :: List a -> Int
length Emp        = 0
length (_ ::: xs) = 1 + length xs
\end{code}

<br>

<div class="fragment">
**Measure**

+ Haskell function with *one equation per constructor*

+ *Strengthens* type of data constructor
