`head` and `tail` are Safe
--------------------------

When called with *non-empty* lists:

<br>

\begin{spec}
{-@ head :: ListNE a -> a @-}
head (x ::: _)  = x
head _          = impossible "head"

{-@ tail :: ListNE a -> List a @-}
tail (_ ::: xs) = xs
tail _          = impossible "tail"
\end{spec}

</div>

